1.5
log
@Change the installation path from /var/www/phpldapadmin-${VERSION} to /var/www/phpldapadmin,
so we don't have to hardcode version numbers everywhere
@
text
@d9 2
a10 5
For jpeg photos to work properly, you must do this:       
	# mkdir /var/www/tmp                 
	# chown www:daemon /var/www/tmp       
	# chmod 1755 /var/www/tmp       
Where tmp is the $jpeg_temp_dir configured in config.php       
@


